site_title: Among Us Paper Airplane by Wilson Lee

block_list.title: Video Tutorial
block_list.body: Among Us there is an imposter!!! I've did it again, I've designed a new Among Us Origami. This is the Among Us paper airplane. This among Us Plane can really fly! It is also the first origami paper plane I have ever designed! I hope you like it. Enjoy! BTW Quickie Version available here : https://youtu.be/KunR_KeUYJk Check out my Among Us Origami play list here https://youtube.com/playlist?list=PL3Ct47F8enQFhzzEz4CHA56TWe3S0sXj4 Thanks for watching! Wilson Lee @Heap Art
